<para style="p">For the chief musician, for Jeduthun. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />I decided, "I will watch what I say</para>

<para style="q1">so that I do not sin with my tongue.</para>

<para style="q1">I will muzzle my mouth</para>

<para style="q1">while in the presence of an evil man."</para>
